    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fool’s Guild is a compact idle economy game that runs beneath your desktop.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manage a small but efficient guild operation while you work, study, or play something else. Your guild keeps progressing quietly in the background — you check in whenever you want.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307320/extras/c56361f10d18f7e99a36d603adc33395.avif?t=1771987765\" width=1560 height=325 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat monsters to collect loot.<br>Grow crops to sell or cook.<br>Feed your miner to extract metals.<br>Forge stronger equipment to push further.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every system feeds another.<br>Everything can be sold.<br>Every decision fuels your expansion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307320/extras/790b0a93070e2c3947c83db2cbd3632b.poster.avif?t=1771987765\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307320/extras/790b0a93070e2c3947c83db2cbd3632b.webm?t=1771987765\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307320/extras/790b0a93070e2c3947c83db2cbd3632b.mp4?t=1771987765\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use Fool’s Coins to unlock new monsters, expand your farm, and increase your production capacity. Balance your resource flow, fine-tune your production chain, and steadily turn a humble guild of fools into a self-sustaining gold machine.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play actively or let it run passively — the choice is yours.<br>Steady progression. Interconnected systems. Background efficiency.</p>",
